# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# EMAIL DELIVERY TO REAL GMAIL INBOXES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# To send confirmation emails that arrive in users' Gmail inboxes:
#
# 1. Go to your Google Account → Security → 2-Step Verification (enable it)
# 2. Go to https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Create a new App Password (select "Mail" and "Other" → name it "FrameMaxx")
# 4. Copy the 16-character password (like: abcd efgh ijkl mnop)
# 5. Paste it below as SMTP_PASS (remove spaces)
#
# Example:
#   SMTP_USER=youremail@gmail.com
#   SMTP_PASS=abcdefghijklmnop
#
# When configured, emails will be sent FROM your Gmail TO the registrant's Gmail.
# When NOT configured, the system uses a test email service (Ethereal) with a
# preview link to view the email in the browser.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=
SMTP_FROM_NAME=FrameMaxx Agency
